{"tid":2296142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原本方國珊都未拉 王百羽就俾人拉先","createTime":"2020-11-22T08:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:59:46.000Z","uid":217049,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69382eaeaa6c13c3f6e5c58f1ed67e869f4018d5","tid":2296142,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:57:33.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉延期，政府早前宣布參選人可獲發還選舉開支，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">當中參選新界東的西貢區議員方國珊申報逾260萬元選舉開支；民主黨林卓廷質疑，當中多項開支未提供單據，亦涉濫報開支</span></strong></span>，稱將要求廉政公署調查，並籲選舉事務處核查單據，以免令人藉選舉申報牟取個人私利。本報正向方國珊查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201011/s00001/1602395596170/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201011%2Fs00001%2F1602395596170%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=7f34dfe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201011%2Fs00001%2F1602395596170%2F&h=76f81965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201011/s00001/1602395596170/</a>"},{"pid":"0c076bda3879eba9ec625009e0f80555e9a1c2b0","tid":2296142,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"如果假博士出聲就會拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805ff3911ab33680a0af13365a96806c32a8c993","tid":2296142,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c076bda3879eba9ec625009e0f80555e9a1c2b0","tid":2296142,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"如果假博士出聲就會拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"公公平平<br />\n有問題都拉晒去調查下"}]}